props.name: steps
props.description: An ordered list of the step names, these values are used for display purposes.

props.name: completedIndex
props.description:
The index of the highest completed step (regardless of the current step the user has selected).
This is used to display the completed steps to the user.

props.name: modelValue
props.description: The index of the step that is currently selected.

events.name: update:modelValue
events.description: Emitted when the selected step is changed.
